WEBVTT

00:00.423 --> 00:02.132
<i>Previously on</i> The Vampire Diaries...

00:02.134 --> 00:03.467
- <i>I'm Sybil.
- We are talking</i>

00:03.492 --> 00:05.873
about a living, breathing siren.

00:05.875 --> 00:09.257
SYBIL: <i>Damon is completely devoted to me.</i>

00:09.259 --> 00:11.993
GEORGIE: <i>This thing, it was delivered
with your vault inhabitant.</i>

00:11.995 --> 00:13.128
<i>I think it was made in hell.</i>

00:13.130 --> 00:14.096
It's a tuning fork.

00:14.098 --> 00:15.263
(ringing)

00:15.265 --> 00:16.765
(yells)

00:16.767 --> 00:17.833
(whimpering)

00:17.835 --> 00:18.967
(grunts)

00:18.969 --> 00:19.968
Damon, it's over.

00:19.970 --> 00:21.069
You're free now.

00:21.071 --> 00:22.437
I wish that were the case, Stefan,

00:22.439 --> 00:24.573
but my work with her is
just getting started.

00:24.575 --> 00:27.027
I really hoped that
when we put Sybil down,

00:27.029 --> 00:28.971
<i>it'd break whatever
control she had over him.</i>

00:28.973 --> 00:31.646
<i>But somehow, some way,
she still has ahold of him.</i>

00:31.648 --> 00:32.981
What else is there to do?

00:32.983 --> 00:35.083
You still have too many attachments.

00:35.085 --> 00:37.252
Too many people willing to fight for you.

00:37.254 --> 00:38.437
<i>We should work on that.</i>

00:38.439 --> 00:39.233
Lockwood.

00:39.235 --> 00:40.429
Damon, wait!

00:41.091 --> 00:42.718
ALARIC: <i>Sirens use mind control</i>

00:42.720 --> 00:44.359
<i>to lure their victims to their death.</i>

00:44.361 --> 00:46.396
Some say they're messengers of the Devil.

00:46.398 --> 00:49.226
<i>I suppose every story
has to start somewhere.</i>

00:57.608 --> 00:59.241
(shivering): Tell me a story.

00:59.243 --> 01:01.410
What kind of story?

01:02.713 --> 01:05.013
Something happy.

01:05.015 --> 01:07.315
A long time ago,

01:07.317 --> 01:08.817
in a village

01:08.819 --> 01:11.153
built on this very spot,

01:11.155 --> 01:13.121
lived a man.

01:13.123 --> 01:14.823
Arcadius.

01:18.662 --> 01:22.631
<i>Cade, to his friends,
of which he had many.</i>

01:22.633 --> 01:25.184
<i>He was a gentle man,</i>

01:25.209 --> 01:28.670
<i>loved and respected.</i>

01:32.697 --> 01:36.111
<i>But Cade could do something
that no one else could:</i>

01:36.113 --> 01:39.830
<i>he could see into the minds of others.</i>

01:41.000 --> 01:47.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

01:49.393 --> 01:50.692
He was psychic?

01:50.694 --> 01:53.395
The first psychic.

01:53.397 --> 01:58.066
It was this power that gave him
so much empathy towards others.

01:58.068 --> 02:02.871
And it was this power that
would cost him his life.

02:20.591 --> 02:22.891
The thing you imagine, brother...

02:24.061 --> 02:26.161
It is impure.

02:26.163 --> 02:27.496
It's forbidden.

02:27.498 --> 02:30.565
If you allow me deeper into your mind,

02:30.567 --> 02:34.069
perhaps I can help quell your urges.

02:34.071 --> 02:36.571
GIRL: <i>Cade had only wanted to help.</i>

02:36.573 --> 02:38.073
<i>But he had overstepped.</i>

02:38.075 --> 02:39.574
(men shouting)

02:39.576 --> 02:40.876
(Cade grunting)

02:40.878 --> 02:42.911
(shouting continues)

02:42.913 --> 02:46.285
<i>And the men, fearing his power,</i>

02:46.310 --> 02:49.417
<i>turned even Cade's friends against him.</i>

02:49.419 --> 02:51.286
(grunting)

02:51.288 --> 02:54.389
<i>And it was then that
Cade came to know</i>

02:54.391 --> 02:55.957
<i>the thing inside men</i>

02:55.959 --> 02:57.459
<i>that even his power</i>

02:57.461 --> 02:59.661
<i>had not been able to divine:</i>

02:59.663 --> 03:01.663
<i>true evil.</i>

03:07.271 --> 03:08.904
(screaming)

03:08.906 --> 03:12.207
I asked for a happy story.

03:12.209 --> 03:14.876
But it is, dear sister.

03:14.878 --> 03:18.547
For in death, Cade was triumphant.

03:18.549 --> 03:20.415
From that moment onward,

03:20.417 --> 03:23.451
evil men would be forever punished

03:23.453 --> 03:25.520
for their wicked deeds.

03:25.522 --> 03:27.589
Cade had his revenge.

03:27.591 --> 03:29.124
And someday,

03:29.126 --> 03:32.460
so will we.

03:40.402 --> 03:44.779
